<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>등록된 글 목록</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial; max-width: 800px; margin: 20px auto; }
    .post { background: white; border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; border-radius: 8px; }
    a { text-decoration: none; color: #1976d2; }
    h1 { font-size: 24px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a href="/">← 글 작성 페이지로 돌아가기</a>
  <h1>📋 등록된 팀플/스터디 모집 글</h1>

  {{#posts}}
    <div class="post">
      <h3>{{title}}</h3>
      <p><strong>과목:</strong> {{subject}} | <strong>작성자:</strong> {{author}} | <strong>날짜:</strong> {{date}}</p>
      <p>{{description}}</p>
    </div>
  {{/posts}}

  {{^posts}}
    <p>아직 등록된 글이 없습니다.</p>
  {{/posts}}
</body>
</html>
